{"tid":2170922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候又要睇下 倪匡當年講中左幾多樣野","createTime":"2020-08-23T14:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T15:46:43.000Z","uid":127454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"86366250d3adbcad3f6daf4fd403edb0bd9e48fb","tid":2170922,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"時代的記錄 - 鏗鏘說：倪匡-無非是這樣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fy8fvjJwmWA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFy8fvjJwmWA&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTPkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=35c63025\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fy8fvjJwmWA</a><br />\n重點 38:06 開始 睇到最尾就啱<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cp98dOF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcp98dOF.png&h=4f976fca&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n其實唔係佢思想行前過好多人 <br />\n只係可能佢直接見識到共產黨係點管治<br />\n而仲有好多人抱住一國可以兩制嘅<del>幻</del>妄想仲未瞓醒<br />\n或者仲妄想緊香港俾共產黨管治會進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇返佢寫追龍呢本<del>小說</del>預言 言論自由已經率先講中 <br />\n淨低嘅可能就係香港未來嘅歷史<br />\n仲有講中啲咩 大家可以講下<br />\n<br />\n最後 當然唔少得呢句經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YsT1yVh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYsT1yVh.png&h=78c3405e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"272b1abfafc902bd4b00268cf19045b3216bbb1b","tid":2170922,"uid":127454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"連登仔又會點評價呢位老人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24a33b6f4ea9438bbf93cb171b9f12bcbf2821a","tid":2170922,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"咪開膠post